text:
Weird Al Yankovic Releases Super Charming Live Music Video for “Tacky” - And I'll have this song stuck in my head for the rest of the day. 
Published By: Geekosystem - Today 
In celebration of the Mandatory Fun world tour, Weird Al has just released a 'live' music video for "Tacky", and it's ridiculously awesome. ...
